<p>
This survey is designed to help us learn more about how people use
VegGuide.Org. This will help guide decisions on future features and
changes.
</p>

<p>
The only identifying information this survey automatically collects is
your IP address. This will not be shared with anyone besides the site
administrator. You may also opt to provide your email address so we
can contact you if we have further questions about your answers.
</p>

